<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.8">
<l>vēta vāymoḻi yantaṇa ṉoruva ṉentai niṉcara ṇeṉṉuṭai maṉaivi</l>
<l>kātal makkaḷaip payattaluṅ kāṇāḷ  kaṭi<supplied>ya</supplied>tōr teyvaṅkoṇṭo ḷikkumeṉ ṟaḻaippa</l>
<l>vēta lārmuṉṉē yiṉṉaru ḷavarkkuc ceytuṉ makkaḷmaṟ ṟivareṉṟu koṭuttāy</l>
<l>āta lālvantu ṉaṭiyiṇai yaṭaintē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkat tammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a priest of the Vedic texts cried out, “Father, [give me] your protection!</l>
<l>As soon as my wife births  our beloved children, [we] do not see [them];</l>
<l rend="indent">a cruel spirit takes and hides [them].”</l>
<l>Performing sweet grace for him right before his foe, you gave [them back] saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Here are your children again”;</l>
<l>Therefore, coming [here], I took refuge at your two feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
